
ZIP
----

	zip is a file not a folder...when we applyzip on any folder its called as file only and it compresses the size


TAR
----
	tar is kind of packing ,in the process of packing little size may reduce ..but not like compressing in zip


ex
---
     tar	    zip
dirx --->  dirx.tar -----> dirx.tar.gz


dirx.tar.gz ----> dirx.tar -----> dirx 
	    unzip	    untar


TO APPLY TAR/zip
--------------
tar-cvf dirx

cvf ---> create verb force

gzip dirx.tar


unzip 
-------
 
 gunzip dirx.tar.gz


 untar
 ------
 tar-xvf dirx.tar

 xvf ---> extract verb force
